  "detailed_description": "►The game is a funny satire on the topic of privacy, people's fear of losing their data<br><br>► It is based on real 20 years of experience in various equipment repair services, and has absorbed many incident situations<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517200/extras/fd630f0879e2d83b0c0339ea1a081715.poster.avif?t=1773613437\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517200/extras/fd630f0879e2d83b0c0339ea1a081715.webm?t=1773613437\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517200/extras/fd630f0879e2d83b0c0339ea1a081715.mp4?t=1773613437\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>►You will have the technical opportunity to interact with the personal data of customers, theoretically you can influence the fate of some inhabitants of this city<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517200/extras/bff49e1777fecc0619dd21f1577f84a2.poster.avif?t=1773613437\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517200/extras/bff49e1777fecc0619dd21f1577f84a2.webm?t=1773613437\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517200/extras/bff49e1777fecc0619dd21f1577f84a2.mp4?t=1773613437\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>►Buy phones from customers and sell excess spare parts, this will help increase income from the workshop<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517200/extras/ca56676a5d6c2e1dc888799c8f84243e.poster.avif?t=1773613437\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517200/extras/ca56676a5d6c2e1dc888799c8f84243e.webm?t=1773613437\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517200/extras/ca56676a5d6c2e1dc888799c8f84243e.mp4?t=1773613437\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>►Getting to know a secret agent can make you an undercover government spy in the form of a master, and of course you will be paid for it<br><br>►Every action you take can have consequences. For example, by copying the genome of a valuable plant, you will help the city with the problem of the food crisis. But don't forget that sometimes even the best deeds can have unexpected consequences",
  "about_the_game": "►The game is a funny satire on the topic of privacy, people's fear of losing their data<br><br>► It is based on real 20 years of experience in various equipment repair services, and has absorbed many incident situations<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517200/extras/fd630f0879e2d83b0c0339ea1a081715.poster.avif?t=1773613437\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517200/extras/fd630f0879e2d83b0c0339ea1a081715.webm?t=1773613437\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517200/extras/fd630f0879e2d83b0c0339ea1a081715.mp4?t=1773613437\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>►You will have the technical opportunity to interact with the personal data of customers, theoretically you can influence the fate of some inhabitants of this city<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517200/extras/bff49e1777fecc0619dd21f1577f84a2.poster.avif?t=1773613437\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517200/extras/bff49e1777fecc0619dd21f1577f84a2.webm?t=1773613437\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517200/extras/bff49e1777fecc0619dd21f1577f84a2.mp4?t=1773613437\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>►Buy phones from customers and sell excess spare parts, this will help increase income from the workshop<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517200/extras/ca56676a5d6c2e1dc888799c8f84243e.poster.avif?t=1773613437\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517200/extras/ca56676a5d6c2e1dc888799c8f84243e.webm?t=1773613437\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2517200/extras/ca56676a5d6c2e1dc888799c8f84243e.mp4?t=1773613437\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>►Getting to know a secret agent can make you an undercover government spy in the form of a master, and of course you will be paid for it<br><br>►Every action you take can have consequences. For example, by copying the genome of a valuable plant, you will help the city with the problem of the food crisis. But don't forget that sometimes even the best deeds can have unexpected consequences",
